'''Kotai Jinja''' (皇大神社) is a Shinto shrine located in Heimamatsuchō, {{ill|Nara Prefecture|ja|奈良県|qq=draft}}{{ill|Nara City|ja|奈良市|qq=draft}}.

== Deities ==
* {{ill|Amaterasu|ja|天照大神|1=Amaterasu|lt=Amaterasu Ōmikami|lqt=Great Sun Spirit|lt_ja=大日霊貴命|qq=draft}}
